  "title": "Business Development Executive (Social Media Marketing) - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><strong>Positon: Business Development Executive</strong></p><ul><li><p>Working Days: Monday - Friday</p></li><li><p>Working Timing: 930am - 630pm</p></li><li><p>Working Location: Maxwell</p></li><li><p>Starting Salary: $5000 - $8000</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>Full job description</strong></em></p><p><em>We are looking for Business Development Specialists to own the sales cycle, from prospecting to onboarding, in the fast-paced and challenging digital sales industry. You will be responsible for building and maintaining the sales pipeline by influencing potential clients to adopt our digital marketing solutions.</em></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Effectively communicate with clients to understand their digital marketing needs and offer solutions to their problems</p></li><li><p>Develope and present proposals customized for each client’s digital marketing needs</p></li><li><p>Prepare and deliver pitches and presentations to prospective clients</p></li><li><p>Handle objections and negotiate with prospective clients</p></li><li><p>Ensure excellent customer relationships through regular follow-up and building rapport with key decision makers</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Knowledge and experience in SEO, GEO, SEM and Social Media Marketing is advantageous<br /></p><p><br /></p></li></ul><p>Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p><p></p>",
